      "delete": {
        "operationId": "delete_agent_secret_beta",
        "summary": "Delete Agent Secret",
        "description": "\n            > \ud83d\udea7 This endpoint is in beta and subject to change.\n            >\n            > A beta revision header (2026-04-15.pre) is required to use our beta APIs. Klaviyo APIs in beta are not intended for use in production. See our [versioning and deprecation policy](https://developers.klaviyo.com/en/docs/api_versioning_and_deprecation_policy) for more information.\n\nPermanently removes the secret.\n\nTools that reference this secret by alias will fail to\nauthenticate on their next call until the alias is rebound to a\ndifferent secret.<br><br>*Rate limits*:<br>Burst: `10/s`<br>Steady: `150/m`\n\n**Scopes:**\n`agents:write`",
